    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>On an ubuntu platform you can use the following command</p>\n\n<pre><code>locate netbeans.conf\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>to find where the netbeans files are located. It's the best way that provides with a precise location of your netbeans.conf file.</p>\n\n<p>Hope this will help someone in need.</p>\n"
